=Episode 18=

14
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,020
Fly.

15
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,220
Fly.

16
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,530
Fly.

17
00:01:52,390 --> 00:01:53,230
Fly.

18
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:55,020
Fly.

19
00:01:55,670 --> 00:01:56,510
Your Majesty.

20
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,410
I'm Shi Yikuan.

21
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:05,160
Greetings, Your Majesty,

22
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,140
Empress Dowager.

23
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,530
Wishing Your Majesty boundless fortune,

24
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:10,340
and the Empress Dowager longevity.

25
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,180
You used to be the Chief Commander,

26
00:02:13,830 --> 00:02:15,380
in charge of Qingzhou.

27
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,530
Now, you're in the capital.

28
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:18,810
Are you used to it?

29
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,250
Whether it's Qingzhou

30
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,620
or the capital,

31
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,970
it's all under the Emperor's rule.

32
00:02:24,830 --> 00:02:27,130
Whether as a commander

33
00:02:27,390 --> 00:02:28,970
or as a minister,

34
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,460
I serve

35
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,660
to manage troops for His Majesty

36
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,180
and relive his worries.

37
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:38,430
Take a seat.

38
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,290
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

39
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:48,510
Your Majesty.

40
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,670
I want some sugary cakes.

41
00:02:51,670 --> 00:02:53,690
You. Get some for me.

42
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:18,730
Are you the leader of Mount Yang,

43
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:20,690
now under imperial pardon?

44
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,530
Thanks to your grace

45
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:24,810
for accepting us,

46
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:26,940
so we can have a chance to return

47
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,250
to the right path.

48
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,920
Take a seat.

49
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:32,230
Thank you.

50
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,620
How handsome.

51
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:44,100
Seems the minister

52
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,970
got a fine son-in-law.

53
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,660
It's all thanks to your favor.

54
00:03:53,990 --> 00:03:54,830
Ziyu,

55
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,800
didn't you prepare a grand gift

56
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,530
for the Empress Dowager?

57
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,810
Seeing

58
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,180
the imperial wealth,

59
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,530
I now

60
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:05,340
feel it's inadequate.

61
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,010
Bring it up.

62
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:30,410
The vital of the North Sea

63
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,820
lies in Mount Ling.

64
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,050
A mountain can only hold one stone.

65
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,290
I think

66
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,050
the Queen Mother nurtures all,

67
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,370
just like you

68
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,780
granted rebirth to Mount Yang.

69
00:04:42,910 --> 00:04:44,370
So, I present this statue

70
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:47,460
to express my determination
to submit to the court.

71
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,730
How could I

72
00:04:52,110 --> 00:04:53,460
ignore your sincerity?

73
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,160
From now on...

74
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,530
The Grand Empress Dowager arrives.

75
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,370
Grand Empress Dowager.

76
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,580
Grandmother.

77
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,320
Grand Empress Dowager

78
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,260
usually stays secluded.

79
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:48,100
Why today, do you
take an interest in coming here?

80
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,780
How thoughtful of you

81
00:06:18,710 --> 00:06:20,120
to remember today

82
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,050
is the late Crown Prince's death anniversary.

83
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,850
You even prepared a banquet.

84
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,820
This...

85
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,050
But the dishes

86
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:33,170
are too heavy.

87
00:06:33,590 --> 00:06:35,900
The colors of the clothes are too bright.

88
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,140
Change them.

89
00:06:43,590 --> 00:06:45,660
Today, the Minister of War assumes office.

90
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:48,490
I specifically summoned him.

91
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:57,730
The late Crown Prince
died suddenly at a prime age,

92
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:01,850
leading to today's situation where you rule

93
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,410
on behalf of the young Emperor.

94
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,370
Today,

95
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,530
instead of mourning him,

96
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:10,970
you are here holding a banquet

97
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:13,460
with a minister.

98
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,820
People will talk.

99
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,290
Empress Dowager,

100
00:07:20,910 --> 00:07:23,780
aren't you afraid?

101
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,970
The late Crown Prince was kind

102
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,530
and an example for all.

103
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,820
No one dares forget his death anniversary.

104
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,220
The Empress Dowager summoned Minister Shi

105
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,830
to remind him

106
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:47,820
to be a kind official,

107
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:49,490
like the late Crown Prince.

108
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,930
As for the dishes and clothes,

109
00:07:53,470 --> 00:07:55,440
while extravagance is
inappropriate on such a day,

110
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,280
neither

111
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:57,820
should we be too frugal.

112
00:07:58,830 --> 00:07:59,920
If the common people think

113
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,000
the treasury is empty,

114
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,930
it might

115
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,660
cause instability and threaten

116
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,340
the foundation of the state.

117
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:07,260
How dare you!

118
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:10,050
The Grand Empress Dowager hasn't spoken yet.

119
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,970
Who allows you to speak?

120
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,730
I didn't expect such talent

121
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,900
from the underworld.

122
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,480
Your Majesty,

123
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:28,660
you value talents.

124
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:31,780
How about appointing him as a secretary

125
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:33,120
in the Ministry of War,

126
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,580
working alongside the Minister?

127
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:39,890
As Mother said.

128
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,420
Thank you, Your Majesty.

129
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:47,420
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

130
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:07,940
(Won.)
Such changes

131
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,890
(Governor committed suicide.)
happened in Xizhou.

132
00:09:10,350 --> 00:09:11,820
According to the letter,

133
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,200
Governor Sheng

134
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,130
likely took his own life out of guilt.

135
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,420
I don't care whether he felt guilty.

136
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,820
Either way, A Gushan was defeated,

137
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,890
bringing glory to the Qi Kingdom.

138
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,180
But it's a pity

139
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,970
that Cui didn't die

140
00:09:27,830 --> 00:09:29,420
on the battlefield.

141
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,240
His victory

142
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:34,060
was merely luck.

143
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:35,650
So what if it was luck?

144
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,300
He'll still enter the capital
triumphantly to present prisoners.

145
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:43,300
Just the thought of having to reward him

146
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,850
makes me sick.

147
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:50,770
If he is rewarded again,

148
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:53,650
I fear the people will only

149
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,610
know Lord Huaiyang

150
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,700
and forget the Emperor.

151
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,130
How dare he!

152
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,010
A lord of a different surname.

153
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,800
I will never let him enter the capital

154
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,060
and threaten the Emperor.

155
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,340
Shi Yikuan.

156
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,460
I value you so much.

157
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,650
What do you think?

158
00:10:17,990 --> 00:10:19,490
I do have a plan,

159
00:10:19,830 --> 00:10:21,850
which I wish to discuss with you.

160
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:28,460
Greetings, Grand Empress Dowager.

161
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,730
Weren't you appointed
as a secretary in the Ministry of War?

162
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:41,130
Why such humility?

163
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:42,850
Without the decree,

164
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,580
I dare not overstep.

165
00:10:46,470 --> 00:10:48,250
In "The Great Perfection of Wisdom Treatise",

166
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,200
it says, "Worst thing happened."

167
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,490
"Best thing didn't."

168
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,540
"Burned by the fire of regret,"

169
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,540
"one falls into the evil path."

170
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:00,300
Have you read the scriptures?

171
00:11:02,590 --> 00:11:03,730
Only scratched the surface.

172
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:06,400
Come closer.

173
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,340
Lift your head.

174
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:31,010
Why did you become a bandit?

175
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:32,850
Parents died early.

176
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:34,540
Nothing left to rely on.

177
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:40,060
I just wanted to survive.

178
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:46,850
I see a kind face,

179
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,700
a bit familiar,

180
00:11:52,230 --> 00:11:53,180
but sadly,

181
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:57,650
you're just a person who follows power,

182
00:11:58,510 --> 00:12:01,130
like your father-in-law Shi Yikuan,

183
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:04,040
flattering

184
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,770
and showing off

185
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:09,730
in front of the Emperor.

186
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:17,850
I have seen too many of your kind.

187
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,700
Your reprimand is justified.

188
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:23,610
Today, I remind you.

189
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:26,890
Aiding the tiger will eventually

190
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:29,250
lead to being harmed by it.

191
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:59,340
(Old friends can't be seen.)

192
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:01,370
(The Hanjiang River flows east.)

193
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:03,940
(For the innocent diseased,)

194
00:13:04,590 --> 00:13:06,100
(I will find the culprit)

195
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,490
(and let them pay with blood.)

196
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,650
(I will avenge you.)

197
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:13,540
(I hope you can rest in peace soon.)

198
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,250
What is happening over there?

199
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,200
This morning,

200
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,890
the Governor's wife invited a ritual.

201
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,700
Now they are distributing porridge.

202
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:35,880
A ritual?

203
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,060
Don't you know?

204
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,320
The Governor died

205
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,580
in his mansion last night.

206
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:42,100
Governor Sheng died?

207
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,240
How did he die?

208
00:13:43,350 --> 00:13:45,420
- No one knows how he died.
- Coming.

209
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,200
Maybe he died from overwork.

210
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,470
He suddenly passed away.

211
00:13:48,470 --> 00:13:50,300
I'll head over there first.

212
00:13:54,470 --> 00:13:56,060
What a sin.

213
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:05,200
Tomorrow, the team

214
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,540
will enter Xizhou City.

215
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:08,770
I hope you will help us

216
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,820
and not make things difficult for my brothers.

217
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:12,440
Mr. Lu, rest assured.

218
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,700
I know what to do.

219
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,100
I'm a night watchman in the city.

220
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,850
After midnight that day,

221
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,220
I was patrolling.

222
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:24,300
The escort team hit me.

223
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:27,010
It's strange enough to escort goods at night,

224
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:28,820
but they were ferocious

225
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,820
and hit me without saying a word.

226
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:34,650
Are you sure it was an escort cart?

227
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:35,680
I'm sure.

228
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,800
Their escort carts and the chests they carried

229
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:38,920
had special markings.

230
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:40,130
I couldn't have mistaken it.

231
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:42,540
Is there

232
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:44,340
anything else unusual?

233
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:46,100
Well...

234
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:49,400
The cart was particularly heavy.

235
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:51,420
The wheels struggled to turn.

236
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,650
No idea what they were transporting.

237
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:54,920
On the side of the cart,

238
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:56,610
something was dripping.

239
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,350
I couldn't see what it was,

240
00:14:58,350 --> 00:15:00,010
but it smelled fishy.

241
00:15:01,590 --> 00:15:02,430
Huang Gui.

242
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:03,760
Take him down.

243
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:04,680
Get an artist to draw

244
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:06,420
everything he described.

245
00:15:06,830 --> 00:15:08,820
Deploy to search the city, inside and out.

246
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:09,950
Yes.

247
00:15:17,470 --> 00:15:19,490
The dripping was human blood.

248
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:21,700
As you said,

249
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:24,010
the Pingyuan Escort Agency was slaughtered.

250
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,750
It rained that night.

251
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,730
Water pooled on the road.

252
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:28,580
Even if there was blood,

253
00:15:28,830 --> 00:15:30,060
it wouldn't show.

254
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:32,650
There's something else

255
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,490
I need your help investigating.

256
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,490
(Qinchang Gate)
With one character,

257
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:39,420
I can tell your fortune.

258
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,610
Yin and yang, five elements.

259
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,340
Nine out of ten readings are accurate.

260
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:46,850
Young lady,

261
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:48,370
would you like to try it?

262
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,340
There are many swindlers.

263
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,460
Madam, don't be deceived.

264
00:16:12,590 --> 00:16:13,820
As you said,

265
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,130
you're nine out of ten accurate.

266
00:16:16,990 --> 00:16:18,580
It means one of them is inaccurate.

267
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:20,490
What if I get that one?

268
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:21,890
Then I won't

269
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:24,490
take your money.

270
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:31,220
Please write a character.

271
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:40,580
(Liu)

272
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:44,310
Done.

273
00:16:48,990 --> 00:16:49,830
Liu means willow.

274
00:16:53,230 --> 00:16:54,580
The willow casts shade.

275
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,340
Shade also means darkness,

276
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:58,820
mostly signifying adversity.

277
00:17:00,470 --> 00:17:02,180
I presume you've been

278
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,840
worried and tired recently,

279
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,300
even facing life-threatening danger,

280
00:17:05,840 --> 00:17:07,130
causing concern

281
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:09,540
among your family.

282
00:17:10,990 --> 00:17:12,840
Sir, you've grasped the cause

283
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:13,930
but not the outcome.

284
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:15,520
As the saying goes,

285
00:17:16,070 --> 00:17:17,500
"The bond of willow is in the tune."

286
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,960
It reflects the bond and longing

287
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,260
between me and my family.

288
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:23,020
Even in peril,

289
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:25,130
I'll find a way out

290
00:17:26,070 --> 00:17:27,260
and survive against the odds.

