- Also.
- Alright.

587
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:53,120
If there are other noodle dishes,
bring them too.

588
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:53,960
No problem.

589
00:32:59,070 --> 00:32:59,910
Nanny Li.

590
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:02,100
Please go call the coachman.

591
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:03,780
I'll take a walk to digest a bit.

592
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:05,450
Alright.

593
00:33:07,870 --> 00:33:10,110
Miss, take a look
at these flower-patterned fabrics.

594
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:14,120
Look at this. All new designs.

595
00:33:15,740 --> 00:33:17,030
This one suits your complexion.

596
00:33:18,990 --> 00:33:21,410
Spare some money, please.

597
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:26,370
Miss, someone is watching you.

598
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:27,890
I know.

599
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:29,850
How did it go?

600
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:32,120
Your suspicion was correct.

601
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:34,130
No one touched the crabapple at the tavern.

602
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:36,340
But at the teahouse next door,

603
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:37,550
a man goes there

604
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:39,020
to have tea every day,

605
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:41,580
staring at the second-floor window
of the tavern.

606
00:33:45,070 --> 00:33:46,890
It's this man with the straw hat.

607
00:33:52,840 --> 00:33:53,680
Follow him.

608
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:55,170
See where he stays.

609
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,610
Be careful.

610
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,680
Mr. Cao.

611
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,990
Lord Huaiyang has found the twenty bodies

612
00:34:23,990 --> 00:34:25,130
from the escort agency.

613
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:28,060
Now, they're searching the city for Qiao Xian.

614
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:30,940
Increase our manpower.

615
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:32,460
We must capture Qiao Xian

616
00:34:32,590 --> 00:34:33,470
before Lord Huaiyang.

617
00:34:33,470 --> 00:34:34,310
Yes.

618
00:34:38,780 --> 00:34:43,140
(Hong House)

619
00:34:43,140 --> 00:34:44,240
Sir.

620
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:45,620
Come on.

621
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:47,000
This way, sir.

622
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,200
Come in, sir.

623
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:49,180
Come on.

624
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:51,620
Sir.

625
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:54,240
Take care, sir.

626
00:34:54,520 --> 00:34:55,560
Take care.

627
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:11,290
Are you going out again?

628
00:35:11,470 --> 00:35:12,360
Do you know

629
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:14,240
your wanted posters are all over the city?

630
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,650
There's a bounty for you.

631
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,810
That's why I can't stay

632
00:35:17,990 --> 00:35:19,860
in one place for long.

633
00:35:23,240 --> 00:35:24,420
If you need money,

634
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:26,100
you can turn me in.

635
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:28,130
What nonsense are you talking about?

636
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:35,250
They won't find me.

637
00:35:35,470 --> 00:35:36,310
Bye.

638
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:52,720
My Lord,

639
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:54,510
your plan worked.

640
00:35:54,510 --> 00:35:55,470
The merchants

641
00:35:55,470 --> 00:35:56,900
aren't interested in the bounty.

642
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,650
When they heard they'd have
to pay the suppression funds,

643
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,330
they started providing leads.

644
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,160
Go.

645
00:36:03,470 --> 00:36:04,310
Bring them in.

646
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:05,910
Yes.

647
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:16,220
(Face-Reading Hall)

648
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:17,390
Master.

649
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,460
I just want to know

650
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,060
if my accumulated merits

651
00:36:21,510 --> 00:36:22,940
are enough to offset my sins.

652
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,770
Too many lies.

653
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,200
It's difficult.

654
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:33,060
I've been looking for you

655
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,940
for a long time.

656
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:37,940
Heaven has eyes.

657
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:43,460
You finally sit before me.

658
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:45,460
Uncle.

659
00:36:46,630 --> 00:36:48,580
I've forgotten the past.

660
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:51,170
What have you been through?

661
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,290
It's a long story.

662
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,280
Everything started

663
00:36:57,670 --> 00:36:59,540
on Shangsi Festival night.

664
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:02,060
(Qiulin Xian)

665
00:37:02,070 --> 00:37:03,020
Do you recognize him?

666
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:05,560
No, I don't.

667
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:06,720
Nonsense!

668
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:08,800
I clearly saw Qiulin Xian

669
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,020
leaving your room.

670
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,460
The cinnabar.

671
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:18,420
I bought it to copy scriptures.

672
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:19,730
I spilled it by accident.

673
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:22,250
What was originally kept here?

674
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:25,060
Nothing.

675
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:27,630
Then how do you explain

676
00:37:27,630 --> 00:37:28,470
this long mark?

677
00:37:29,240 --> 00:37:31,980
Maybe something fell on the floor.

678
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:33,610
I don't know.

679
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:37,950
Huang Gui.

680
00:37:39,470 --> 00:37:41,020
What does this sheet

681
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,130
look like to you?

682
00:37:47,150 --> 00:37:48,020
It looks like...

683
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:58,380
After I woke up,

684
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:01,130
I only remembered that I was to marry Cui Jiu.

685
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:02,880
That's the man

686
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:04,760
I now call my husband every day.

687
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:06,210
But he's not Cui Jiu.

688
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:07,810
I didn't know that at the time.

689
00:38:07,990 --> 00:38:09,540
I even mistook him.

690
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,480
He used my amnesia,

691
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,540
deceiving me

692
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:14,650
into thinking we had a marital relationship.

693
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:17,070
He trapped me in a house

694
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:18,100
in Lingquan Town,

695
00:38:19,070 --> 00:38:20,290
but he also believed

696
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:22,380
that I was Lu Wen's concubine,

697
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:24,690
so he used me as bait

698
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:26,500
to capture Lu Wen.

699
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:34,860
(Face-Reading Hall)

700
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:40,220
(Face-Reading Hall)

701
00:38:40,720 --> 00:38:41,560
Let's go in.

702
00:38:41,590 --> 00:38:42,430
Yes.

703
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:43,870
Mantang,

704
00:38:44,470 --> 00:38:45,690
you are naturally sharp.

705
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:48,940
Do you know who this Cui Jiu really is?

706
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:51,770
I'll find out

707
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:54,170
who he is.

708
00:38:54,720 --> 00:38:55,590
I'll settle the score

709
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:56,690
with him.

710
00:38:57,550 --> 00:38:59,540
As for how he used me in the past,

711
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:03,060
I'll repay him in full.

712
00:39:14,110 --> 00:39:14,950
But right now,

713
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,580
I have more important things.

714
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:19,980
The person who killed our escort brothers

715
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:21,810
is the one

716
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,210
who severed my tendons

717
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:25,130
and caused my fall and amnesia.

718
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:27,290
He's now searching for you, Uncle.

719
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,290
Until he's dead,

720
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:31,170
I won't find peace.

721
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,640
Master,

722
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:34,650
is there really no way to remedy this?

723
00:39:36,470 --> 00:39:37,650
Well...

724
00:39:40,720 --> 00:39:41,770
Master.

725
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:47,200
Honey.

726
00:39:51,240 --> 00:39:52,380
Why are you here, dear?

727
00:39:54,670 --> 00:39:55,510
Master,

728
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:57,770
today I accompanied the madam

729
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:59,290
to have face-reading.

730
00:40:02,360 --> 00:40:04,460
Are you here on official business?

731
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:05,560
Yes.

732
00:40:07,240 --> 00:40:09,900
How accurate is the fortune-telling?

733
00:40:16,630 --> 00:40:17,470
Very accurate.

734
00:40:18,030 --> 00:40:20,210
He said you are kind-hearted,

735
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,500
honest, and straightforward,

736
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,900
and that your official career will be smooth.

737
00:40:24,190 --> 00:40:25,030
He even predicted

738
00:40:25,030 --> 00:40:25,900
your promotion.

739
00:40:34,720 --> 00:40:35,580
Come on, honey.

740
00:40:45,550 --> 00:40:46,390
Master.

741
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:52,650
While your official career is promising,

742
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:55,900
I'm afraid your noble star conflicts

743
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,280
with the solitary star,

744
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:59,060
making it difficult to rise to great heights.

745
00:41:00,670 --> 00:41:02,760
Honey, since we're here,

746
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:04,170
why don't you ask the master

747
00:41:04,670 --> 00:41:06,860
to check our marriage compatibility?

748
00:41:07,030 --> 00:41:08,030
It won't take long.

749
00:41:08,030 --> 00:41:09,170
You won't delay your work.

750
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,210
A face reading?

751
00:41:18,880 --> 00:41:20,060
You two

752
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:23,380
are a match made in heaven.

753
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,420
That seems accurate.

754
00:41:28,030 --> 00:41:28,990
Now, I want to know

755
00:41:28,990 --> 00:41:30,540
about the future of our marriage.

756
00:41:31,280 --> 00:41:33,650
Then please draw a lot.

757
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:44,660
(Lot 1: Most Auspicious)

758
00:41:53,260 --> 00:41:55,180
(Lot 18: Most Inauspicious)

759
00:41:58,720 --> 00:41:59,810
Most inauspicious.

760
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,130
What does it mean?

761
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:08,130
A clear path ahead, but suddenly it turns dark.

762
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:11,730
Don't pursue what's unclear.

763
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:16,100
A crumbling wall returns to dust.

764
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:19,900
Even with divine help, it won't stand.

765
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:23,580
If this lot is interpreted for marriage,

766
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,130
it foretells difficulties.

767
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,770
Do you

768
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:31,060
have any secrets between you?

769
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:34,170
- I don't.
- No.

770
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,420
Then it must be

771
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,130
the lot falling to the ground,

772
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:41,380
affected by the earth's energy.

773
00:42:42,150 --> 00:42:44,650
If we interpret it by the lot's words,

774
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:47,580
you may love each other,

775
00:42:48,110 --> 00:42:50,100
but without honesty,

776
00:42:50,720 --> 00:42:53,170
you will drift apart.

777
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,940
Is there any chance to turn things around?

778
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:57,380
This

779
00:42:58,030 --> 00:42:59,540
is fate.

780
00:43:00,630 --> 00:43:01,540
However,

781
00:43:01,960 --> 00:43:04,770
fate can be changed by people.

782
00:43:05,110 --> 00:43:08,100
As long as you are sincere with each other,

783
00:43:08,670 --> 00:43:11,900
there will be a chance to win each other back.

784
00:43:14,670 --> 00:43:15,510
Dear,

785
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:18,020
I will be honest with you.

786
00:43:19,240 --> 00:43:20,130
I will too.

787
00:43:36,100 --> 00:43:42,330
♪The boat drifts,
bringing back the sunset♪

788
00:43:43,330 --> 00:43:49,450
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

789
00:43:50,440 --> 00:43:56,690
♪Who passed by, the crabapple
falls with a turn♪

790
00:43:57,820 --> 00:44:01,060
♪Loving rightly but choosing wrong♪

791
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:05,980
♪With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

792
00:44:06,580 --> 00:44:13,240
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

793
00:44:13,990 --> 00:44:17,360
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

794
00:44:17,650 --> 00:44:20,980
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

795
00:44:21,160 --> 00:44:27,930
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

796
00:44:28,310 --> 00:44:35,080
♪Long hidden in the eyes,
flickering in and out♪

797
00:44:35,580 --> 00:44:41,990
♪Let go of the flowers blooming
in the yard last night♪

798
00:44:42,830 --> 00:44:49,240
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

799
00:44:49,820 --> 00:44:56,440
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

800
00:44:57,240 --> 00:45:00,660
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky♪

801
00:45:00,660 --> 00:45:05,760
♪There are many more♪

802
00:45:06,140 --> 00:45:12,860
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

803
00:45:13,430 --> 00:45:17,060
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

804
00:45:17,060 --> 00:45:20,460
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

805
00:45:20,460 --> 00:45:27,370
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

806
00:45:27,660 --> 00:45:34,510
♪Time flows as we dream through four seasons♪

807
00:45:34,880 --> 00:45:38,460
♪I wish to journey with you forever♪

808
00:45:38,460 --> 00:45:41,570
♪Year after year♪

809
00:45:43,300 --> 00:45:47,600
♪For many years to come♪
